OL,7,FLaurence Fox has lost a libel battle
OL,8,Fwith two people he referred to as
OL,9,Fpaedophiles on social media.
OL,11,FThe actor-turned-politician was sued
OL,12,Fby former Stonewall trustee Simon
OL,13,FBlake and drag artist Crystal over a
OL,14,Frow on X, formerly Twitter, in October
OL,15,F2020.
