OL,7,FMr Fox called Mr Blake and the
OL,8,FRuPaul's Drag Race contestant, whose
OL,9,Freal name is Colin Seymour,
OL,10,F"paedophiles" in an exchange about a
OL,11,Fdecision by Sainsbury's to mark Black
OL,12,FHistory Month.
OL,14,FThe Reclaim Party founder ` who said
OL,15,Fat the time that he would boycott the
OL,16,Fsupermarket ` counter-sued the pair
OL,17,Fand broadcaster Nicola Thorp over
OL,18,Ftweets accusing him of racism.
