OL,7,FIn a ruling on Monday, High Court
OL,8,Fjudge Mrs Justice Collins Rice ruled
OL,9,Fin favour of Mr Blake and Mr Seymour,
OL,10,Fdismissing Mr Fox's counter-claims.
OL,12,FShe said: "Mr Fox's labelling of Mr
OL,13,FBlake and Mr Seymour as paedophiles
OL,14,Fwas, on the evidence, probabilities
OL,15,Fand facts of this case, seriously
OL,16,Fharmful, defamatory and baseless.
OL,18,F"The law affords few defences to
OL,19,Fdefamation of this sort.
OL,26,@tD@KOUzD@AOU
