OL,7,FIn his written evidence for the case,
OL,8,FMr Seymour, a Canadian artist, said he
OL,9,Fhad faced "overwhelming and
OL,10,Fdistressing" abuse after Mr Fox's
OL,11,Ftweet, adding that he felt less safe
OL,12,Fas a drag performer.
OL,14,FMr Blake, now chief executive of
OL,15,FMental Health First Aid England, said
OL,16,Fthe incorrect suggestion that gay men
OL,17,Fare paedophiles is "a trope as old as
OL,18,Fthe hills".
