OL,7,FHowever, Patrick Green KC,
OL,8,Frepresenting Mr Fox, told the court
OL,9,Fthat neither Mr Blake nor Mr Seymour
OL,10,F"has suffered any actual, real-world
OL,11,Fconsequences" due to the actor's
OL,12,Ftweets.
OL,14,FMr Fox told the court he was
OL,15,F"horrified" when he saw he had been
OL,16,Fcalled a racist, which he later
OL,17,Fdescribed as "a career-ending word and
OL,18,Fa reputation-destroying allegation".
