OL,7,FThe actor said he faced a "significant
OL,8,Fdecline" in the number and quality of
OL,9,Froles he was offered after he was
OL,10,Faccused of being a racist in the
OL,11,Fsocial media row.
OL,13,FIn the 41-page ruling, Justice Collins
OL,14,FRice said it would be "extremely long
OL,15,Fodds" for the tweets of the three
OL,16,Fpeople sued by Mr Fox to have caused
OL,17,Fthe current state of his acting
OL,18,Fcareer, or other serious harm.
