OL,7,FShe continued: "It is not only what he
OL,8,Fsays, but how he says it, that
OL,9,Fregularly ignites controversy around
OL,10,FMr Fox, deliberately or otherwise."
OL,12,FMr Fox said he will appeal the
OL,13,Fdecision, "to get a meaning" to the
OL,14,Fword racist.
OL,16,F"What is a racist? Every single person
OL,17,Fin this country knows what a racist
OL,18,Fis, except the people that dominate
OL,19,Fevery single national institution that
OL,20,Fwe have."
