OL,7,FMeanwhile, Ms Thorp said the trio won
OL,8,F"on all counts" in a celebration post
OL,9,Fto X.
OL,11,FMr Seymour separately posted: "I am
OL,12,Fincredibly relieved to have this
OL,13,Foutcome ` a huge weight I've been
OL,14,Fcarrying for over three years has just
OL,15,Fbeen lifted.
OL,17,F"I want to say again that I took no
OL,18,Fjoy in bringing this case, nor did I
OL,19,Fdo so lightly. Mr Fox could have made
OL,20,Fthis go away very early on with a
OL,21,Fmeaningful apology and settlement."
